3e8ed4213ae58","tid":1364770,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:37:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be2cd02be5a3dfa394e3486e13d200a877c2ab23","tid":1364770,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"屌你 不篤灰呀<br />\n你想變左連登 被人針？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81035b307f407a59e5302d0ccb147bef30ea684","tid":1364770,"uid":54593,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:38:02.000Z","msg":"其實最近個個部門遍地開花，寫公開信表態，如果佢地肯做多步帶頭罷工，效果一定勝百倍"},{"pid":"36bdd9f1d5f33e205023894fd800e68a94524902","tid":1364770,"uid":76310,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:40:59.000Z","msg":"做唔到<br />\n<br />\n你明白香港個社會經濟結構就知不太可能"},{"pid":"ab536095dd469b7a464150e6835ba819dcff5af9","tid":1364770,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"66618879e832efded64c1dd44d2c0bce94e8b575","tid":1364770,"uid":258758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8289903f5798232619457fff2505bf34eb19ec21","tid":1364770,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:26:04.000Z","msg":"呢招work"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:34:40.000Z","msg":"公務員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:42:41.000Z","msg":"Work"},{"pid":"afd8c6932dd7a7e60f573b5f419706acb4633c32","tid":1364770,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:43:48.000Z","msg":"反送中咁耐以嚟，有人發起罷工，又最多人響應<br />\n已經係617？<br />\n成效係點？只係自己打下J咋<br />\n<br />\n仲要根本好多人唔係罷工<br />\n係請一日假/ 扮病/銷下假<br />\n然後第二日又繼續返工<br />\n<br />\n罷工有用，只有喺工會同公司講數時，先最有用<br />\n例如空姐，巴士司機等等公共事務服務業<br />\n先有用，因為公司高層要提供正常服務就會就範<br />\n咁先有數講<br />\n<br />\n集體罷工呢招對林鄭永遠唔work <br />\n就算有原因令香港人嬲到集體罷工，都要係60%以上肯罷工，講明罷到政府回應先返工，先有機會<br />\n而做到呢個效果，相信都已經唔係市民罷工俾到壓力政府<br />\n而係跌市，啲有錢佬大粒佬有經濟損失下俾壓力政府<br />\n呢個官商勾結嘅政府先初做嘢，再向北大人跪地先有機會<br />\n<br />\n而喺香港人大多數打工仔，都唔係做公共事業服務<br />\n例如做飲食，做sales，做保險，你罷工，政府唔撚怕你<br />\n佢唔係你老闆佢理撚後你<br />\n總有其他食店有提供服務<br />\n罷嗰啲有機會俾人炒<br />\n搵食對熱血年青人來講，唔係最重要<br />\n但要養家嘅人，轉工都要等時機啦，手停口停好大鑊<br />\n而且好多人要供樓，陷家要養"},{"pid":"80778ea4dd7b9ee06a66c706e59c7d5138341037","tid":1364770,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:45:45.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 隨遇而安的人"},{"pid":"1dc7ab7de337b447774419f1915b3672eb62ef6b","tid":1364770,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"山竹攪到香港世界末日咁, 個個都要趕住番工, 排除萬難<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180917/large/1537175792_c9b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180917%2Flarge%2F1537175792_c9b0.jpg&h=89d1d881&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1759038a17dba6ee4ffa2326c6035bd8a1b416cf","tid":1364770,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:46:21.000Z","msg":"你咪Block, 以事論事"},{"pid":"536f64a951c3cccc9ae626639bef4f19e7fbaa2e","tid":1364770,"uid":265066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:46:43.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b8c0640bb50d56ff9052e25673804df6d1d1e8","tid":1364770,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2018/9/1537255371_Hn-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2018%2F9%2F1537255371_Hn-1280w.jpg&h=10c0e2f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/09/20/385795/i_640x1140_704161594.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F09%2F20%2F385795%2Fi_640x1140_704161594.jpg&h=924e350a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.